title: [Trading Post, Trophy Room]
description: Stuffed and mounted creatures serve as decoration in this musty room.  Moonlight streams in through a shuttered window in the west wall.  A soft couch and several comfortable chairs are available for prolonged viewing of the trophies.  A wide variety of weapons adorn the walls, some in display cases, others simply hung by nails.
